org.apache.poi.hssf.record

Class CommonObjectDataSubRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.SubRecord
      • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.CommonObjectDataSubRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Duplicatable, GenericRecord 

    public final class CommonObjectDataSubRecord
extends SubRecord
    The common object data record is used to store all common preferences for an excel object.(公用对象数据记录用于存储Excel对象的所有公用首选项。)

      • getDataSize

        protected int getDataSize()
        Specified by:
        getDataSize in class SubRecord(SubRecord类中的getDataSize)
        Returns:
        the size of the data for this record (which is always 4 bytes less than the total record size). Note however, that ushort encoded after the record sid is usually but not always the data size.(此记录的数据大小（始终比总记录大小小4个字节）。不过请注意，记录sid之后编码的ushort通常是但不总是数据大小。)
